    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>安装准备</h2>

<ol>
<li>jdk</li>
<li>maven</li>
<li><a href="http://www.sonatype.com/download-oss-sonatype">Nexus Repository Manager OSS 2.xx</a></li>
</ol>


<h2>解压并运行服务</h2>

<p>将下载的nexus-2.13.0-01-bundle.tar.zip包解压到特定的目录，这里是/Applications/
